{"tid":1308812,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"點解要分 主線支線","createTime":"2019-07-12T03:43:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-12T04:11:23.000Z","uid":12179,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"696995de98b1d29aaefec9025dd95295caa96fba","tid":1308812,"uid":12179,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T03:43:43.000Z","msg":"主線:一定要做<br />\n支線:有時間，有心力先做<br />\n唔好因爲做支線而做唔到主線<br />\n<br />\n我相信大部分人其實做支線既一定會做主線，冇錯兄弟爬山各有各做，但問題係推支線post既同時令主線post沉哂，變相少左人睇到，尤其係光復遊行集會既行動，人數係最重要，大家可以睇下依家熱門有冇713 714既post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n近日好多因為連儂牆而嘈亦係呢個原因，大家見到d負面post不妨ignore，不如用時間推返d主線，尤其需要人數既行動，記住連登仲有好多CD-ROM，要令佢地見到。<br />\n<br />\n「跪求置頂」【任務欄】 快啲入嚟 吾好淨係做支線 我哋要推主線任務 然後打波Boss<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1306215\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1306215</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n有巴打已經分好哂主線支線，推返d主線post上熱門，等多d人睇到！<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">五大訴求 對準政權<br />\n兄弟爬山 各自努力<br />\n不分化 不割蓆</span></strong>"},{"pid":"fb279e355fdbd40509d0c8d153947d555d7ce412","tid":1308812,"uid":75959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T03:44:47.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">保持獨立思考 唔好比敵人 輕易帶風向帶走左</span></span>"},{"pid":"e4dd883e73dbdb6abc8fb95ae4f3dbe23ed703ce","tid":1308812,"uid":14026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T03:45:23.000Z","msg":"岩"},{"pid":"299f297dd94f57ac9d6ef929845dbbc769a5da6b","tid":1308812,"uid":77092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T03:45:51.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a7e05a183303245ffd553e9b43832ec2186c5eb1","tid":1308812,"uid":77092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T03:46:09.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8b6df747a293318cafa6536f177c6a16f4168332","tid":1308812,"uid":62270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T04:11:23.000Z","msg":"岩"}]}